   NAME:      Pkg_RTCM0205
   PURPOSE:   문자포맷 Detail 관리

   REVISIONS:
   Ver        Date        Author           Description
   ---------  ----------  ---------------  -------------------------------------
   1.0        2023-01-31  kstka            1. Created this package body.
